  "name": "千夜浮夢",
  "desc": "<p>浮映千夜之夢的燈盞，蒼翠的光中流溢著遙世的歌。</p>",
  "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/7998136/afd146c520b3a0bd72489a3426d8f283_2843731128544519943.png",
